title: Pusey, Haute-Saône
text: Pusey () is a <a href="Communes%20of%20France">commune</a> in the <a href="Haute-Sa%C3%B4ne">Haute-Saône</a> <a href="Departments%20of%20France">department</a> in the <a href="Regions%20of%20France">region</a> of <a href="Bourgogne-Franche-Comt%C3%A9">Bourgogne-Franche-Comté</a> in eastern <a href="France">France</a>.
